Usage: all_outputs [-help] [-clock <list_of_clocks>] [-edge_triggered  | -level_sensitive ]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-clock <list_of_clocks>     # Considers only output ports with an output delay
                            # relative to a specific list of clocks
                            # (string, optional)
-edge_triggered             # Returns a collection of output ports with the
                            # set_output_delay -clock constraint (bool, optional)
-level_sensitive            # Returns a collection of output ports with the
                            # set_output_delay -level_sensitive constraint
                            # (bool, optional)